content.raw: I’ve seen this happening from time to time. I believe everything should be functional.

content.raw:
The IMU test on homebrew failed with lots of these messages:

`[Err] [ImuSensor.cc:100] Not initialized, update ignored.`

I assume we need a new `ign-sensors` bottle...?
